00:19:21,320 --> 00:19:24,360
So I can't answer that question.

232
00:19:24,520 --> 00:19:28,440
But the development we see is alarming.

233
00:19:28,600 --> 00:19:33,480
From Klys and my work I can say -

234
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:38,760
–Ad every time the freedom of speech is limited we react -

235
00:19:38,920 --> 00:19:44,440
- And trying to oppose us that development in referral opinions and other things.

236
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:47,600
Do you then think of the political governance -

237
00:19:47,760 --> 00:19:52,640
