238
00:19:52,800 --> 00:19:57,160
I think of the political governance -

239
00:19:57,320 --> 00:20:02,120
- But also on what Kerstin was in, the conditions of the cultural creator.

240
00:20:02,280 --> 00:20:06,240
That the conditions look like this today-

