245
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:28,480
Freedom of speech and political governance often collapse.

246
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:33,440
As Ulrica says, self -censorship is an almost equal threat -

247
00:20:33,600 --> 00:20:37,320
- As a kind of political restriction on freedom of expression.

248
00:20:37,480 --> 00:20:40,400
I have seen ROP - for a number of years

249
00:20:40,560 --> 00:20:45,560
- On the fact that one should restrict the possibilities of commenting in the public space.

250
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:52,720
On Dagens Nyheter's cultural site, we have been able to read calls for private companies -

251
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:57,720
