252
00:20:57,880 --> 00:21:01,800
The sitting government had a meeting with Youtube -

253
00:21:01,960 --> 00:21:06,680
- About how to limit access to dissatisfied views.

254
00:21:06,840 --> 00:21:11,520
On Youtube it is the same group ...

255
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:15,080
This has a number of strange consequences.

256
00:21:15,240 --> 00:21:22,640
On Facebook, people can come together against political opponents with mass notifications -

257
00:21:22,800 --> 00:21:30,000
- And then Facebook removes the posts or even closes by people.

258
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:35,840
