259
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:41,120
On Youtube we have seen how counterproductive this will be.

260
00:21:41,280 --> 00:21:46,480
You may read about the Swedish Democrats' film about the Social Democrats -

261
00:21:46,640 --> 00:21:51,240
