264
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:08,080
On the one hand, the debate was not about whether the image they conveyed in their film was true -

265
00:22:08,240 --> 00:22:12,040
- Out whether they had been silenced.

266
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:16,560
So even opponents of the Sweden Democrats shot themselves in the foot -

267
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:19,960
- When their film was removed.

268
00:22:20,120 --> 00:22:26,480
There are many examples where one supposedly good purpose -

269
00:22:26,640 --> 00:22:30,640
