270
00:22:30,800 --> 00:22:37,520
The Facebook algorithm's change in February this year when you were to make Facebook more enjoyable.

271
00:22:37,680 --> 00:22:43,560
Zuckerberg's purpose was that we would not get irrelevant things in our flows.

