00:24:14,240 --> 00:24:18,680
- And other types of interest organizations in cultural bureaucratic field.

291
00:24:18,840 --> 00:24:23,280
We fast in a contradiction between artistic practice and cultural bureaucracy -

292
00:24:23,440 --> 00:24:25,920
