293
00:24:26,080 --> 00:24:31,640
Kerstin talked about the fact that there is a void that the policy leaves there now.

294
00:24:31,800 --> 00:24:36,120
I also identify that void in the art.

295
00:24:36,280 --> 00:24:39,680
I am a primarily performing artist.

296
00:24:39,840 --> 00:24:44,880
Although I have been a manager for about fifteen years, I can see -

297
00:24:45,040 --> 00:24:50,160
