00:27:34,880 --> 00:27:40,080
But in the production of art, in the collaboration ...

331
00:27:40,240 --> 00:27:44,520
Then all support systems have a tendency to become guiding -

332
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:49,440
- Propping of self -censorship, and therefore you need to discuss them.

333
00:27:49,600 --> 00:27:54,960
If I am going to take on the fundamentalists that we have not represented in the panel -

334
00:27:55,120 --> 00:28:00,000
- So they would say that when we instrumentalize the art expressions in that way -

335
00:28:00,160 --> 00:28:05,360
–And says things that are okay at this time as it can be a danger -

