00:28:05,520 --> 00:28:09,480
- As every time has its taboos.

337
00:28:09,640 --> 00:28:15,600
Now we have broken a taboo with "metoo" that you couldn't talk about five to ten years ago-

338
00:28:15,760 --> 00:28:19,680
- And could not express in any way.
 What do you say about it?

339
00:28:19,840 --> 00:28:24,760
There has never been any legislation against talking about Metoo.

340
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:28,720
It has been a norm simply -

341
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:33,800
–And that's what I think is interesting, in what you said Kerstin -

342
00:28:33,960 --> 00:28:40,680
- If we must be able to create reasonable production conditions and working conditions.

343
00:28:40,840 --> 00:28:44,720
It has nothing to do with what is then said in the art.

344
00:28:44,880 --> 00:28:47,360
Absolutely nothing.

345
00:28:47,520 --> 00:28:52,880
We are still living in a mythology of a little worse working conditions -

346
00:28:53,040 --> 00:28:57,520
- There is a little "ruff" climate, provides better art.

347
00:28:57,680 --> 00:29:04,120
I have worked for 20 years as a director and am a living proof that it is not true.

348
00:29:04,280 --> 00:29:08,840
Had it been, I would not have been in the profession.

349
00:29:09,000 --> 00:29:13,920
If it had been a compulsion to have poor working conditions.

350
00:29:14,080 --> 00:29:21,480
I think that within the artistic we actually need to evaluate -

351
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:25,720
- This is the structure and not the content.

352
00:29:25,880 --> 00:29:29,160
Thus, the structure for collaboration and so on.

