00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:15,760
– That one shifts power from civil society and the private sector -

363
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:18,640
- To public institutions.

364
00:30:18,800 --> 00:30:24,280
I rather believe that there is a danger there, due to public institutions -

365
00:30:24,440 --> 00:30:31,320
- All time will reproduce the values of political power that prevail at the moment.

366
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:37,160
The only way to counteract this is institutional competition -

367
00:30:37,320 --> 00:30:42,640
- Over if we talk about private or publicly funded institutions.

