370
00:30:51,080 --> 00:30:56,640
- Yes, it would be good if there was one for cultural council.
 - Attach, then!

371
00:30:56,800 --> 00:31:00,880
Artistic freedom occurs in the space between the institutions.

372
00:31:01,040 --> 00:31:06,080
You can never order artistic freedom from a political point of view.

373
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:09,960
What you can do is not limit artistic freedom.

374
00:31:10,120 --> 00:31:14,520
Do you want a reply?
 You get it.

375
00:31:14,680 --> 00:31:19,040
We think it is good that there are several authorities -

376
00:31:19,200 --> 00:31:23,360
–Or works with the field of cultural and artist policy-

377
00:31:23,520 --> 00:31:29,800
- Because we complement each other, have different knowledge and support different parts of the area.

378
00:31:33,240 --> 00:31:38,920
I just want to say that the state has a great responsibility, as well as regions and municipalities.

379
00:31:39,080 --> 00:31:42,360
But the private, you ...

380
00:31:42,520 --> 00:31:47,640
Private donors have a huge responsibility -

381
00:31:47,800 --> 00:31:53,640
