388
00:32:28,120 --> 00:32:31,680
–Bae by the state expanding its commitments -

389
00:32:31,840 --> 00:32:35,760
- And that they undermined the opportunities for private financing.

390
00:32:35,920 --> 00:32:39,040
So it was a two -way process.

391
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:45,240
