00:36:17,400 --> 00:36:22,360
How should we fulfill the idea that I think many of us share -

437
00:36:22,520 --> 00:36:28,440
- If as many people as possible should be able to take part in as much culture and art as possible?

438
00:36:28,600 --> 00:36:34,120
It is also a prerequisite that the participants, the visitors, the audience ...

439
00:36:34,280 --> 00:36:38,560
What you now do for the type of art.
 The viewers.

